" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Jersey finger examination",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 360px; height: 415px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Loss of flexion&nbsp;at the distal interphalangeal (DIP) joint of the ring finger is seen&nbsp;when the patient actively makes a fist, suggesting a flexor tendon injury of the DIP joint&nbsp;(ie, Jersey finger).&nbsp;",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
